    * added include files:
      + wxh/socket.ch
      + wxh/gsocket.ch

  * include/event.ch
  * src/common/sysdefs.cpp
    ! Fixed several wxEVT_* defines (Linux/Win)

  * include/wxharbour.ch
  * src/common/wxhfuncs.prg
    * added code to set NIL to the obj variable in DESTROY command
    * added ACTION clause to @ GET command
    - removed REFRESH ALL clause on @ GET command
    * added @ TEXTCTRL command

  * samples/networking/simple.prg
    * updated sample code

  * src/common/wx_harbour.cpp
    + added wxWidgets functions:
      + wxMutexGuiEnter
      + wxMutexGuiLeave

      * this functions are needed when updates to GUI are executed
        from a thread other than main thread

  * src/hrbcompat/misc/wxGET.prg
    % added connectEvt to update var when ENTER key is pressed
      improvements made to update proces

  * src/wxbase/networking/wxhSocketBase.prg
  * src/wxbase/networking/wx_SocketBase.cpp
    * renamed wxError method name to Error
    * borrowed hb_itemReSizeString from Harbour Project, this function
      is missed in xHarbour

      ; Thanks to the Harbour Project Team

    ! Fixed bug on Read/ReadMsg functions, now just one parameter can
      be used in the caller construction, the size of the buffer is
      adjusted if second parameter is issued (size)

        size = ISNIL( 2 ) ? pBuffer->item.asString.length : hb_parnl( 2 )

      The size of the buffer is resized accordingly to the size obtained

    * code cleanup

  + tests
  + tests/evtdefcheck
