  * src/hrbcompat/tbrowse/wxhbrowsedbprovider.prg
  * src/hrbcompat/tbrowse/wxhbrowse.prg
    * implemented TBrowse *alike*:
      DATA cargo, GoBottomBlock, GoTopBlock, SkipBlock
      PROPERTY ColCount, RowCount, ColPos, RowPos
      METHOD AddColumn( column ), DelColumn( pos ), Down, GoBottom, GoTop
        PageDown, PageUp, RefreshAll, Up
    ; I don't want to achieve 100% of TBrowse compat, only to give
      a very close functionality.

