    * renamed class wxColumn to wxhBColumn (Browse Column)
    * renamed function wxColumnNew() to wxhBColumnNew()

  * src/hrbcompat/tbrowse/wx_browse.cpp
  * src/hrbcompat/tbrowse/wx_browse.h
    * renamed class from wx_Browse to wxBrowse
    * added event c++ handler to intercept changes on grid size (vertical ones to us)
    * added wxhBrowse::CalcRowCount() to get available rows on grid (browse)
    * added c++ class initializer from hb (wxNew)
  * src/hrbcompat/tbrowse/wxhbrowse.prg
    * blocked calls to AppendCols,AppendRows ..., we need only the harbour methods
    + added TBrowse compat methods
      + RowCount
      + AddColumn
      + DelColumn
      + GoBottom
      + GoTop
    * wxhBrowse is constructed within a wxPanel and has a vert scroll bar, the
      grid (browse) has a fixed number of rows (RowCount) and the additional
      scroll bar is for navigation control.
    + added
      + AddAllColumns : currently to poblate cols from an TTable object
    % several major enhancements

  * src/wxbase/advctrls/wx_grid.cpp
    * code cleanup to pacify MSVC compiler with 'assignament on conditional...'
    + added
      + GetNumberCols, GetNumberRows
      + IsVisible

